bmc software specializes in the development  marketing and maintenance of systems software products for large enterprises operating ibm and ibm compatible mainframes or client server information systems 
the company is currently offering software products  of which are mainframe products and are client server products 
the company s core business is the provision of high performance utilities and administrative tools for the primary high end ibm mainframe database management systems  ims and db in each of the last three fiscal years  these products generated approximately of the company s total revenues and higher percentages of its earnings 
