an enterprise license typically requires an evaluation of the customer s processing capacity level periodically throughout the term of the agreement or at the end of the term 
the licensee is required to pay additional charges if the mips capacity on which the licensed products are being used exceeds the stipulated processing capacity level previously purchased 
